{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="row">
    <div class="shortcut-wrap">
      <div class="shortcut-rail">
        <a href="/faq.html" class="shortcut-item">
          <span><i class="fa-regular fa-circle-question"></i></span>
          <p>FAQ</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/technical-support.html" class="shortcut-item">
          <span><i class="fa-regular fa-headset"></i></span>
          <p>Technical Support</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/live-chat.html" class="shortcut-item">
          <span><i class="fa-regular fa-messages"></i></span>
          <p>Live Chat</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact-us.html" class="shortcut-item">
          <span><i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i></span>
          <p>Contact Us</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="white-box mb-5">
        <h1 class="h1 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-4">Find answers to common questions about admissions, academics, and student services.</p>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 mb-4">
            <div class="white-box">
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Admissions & Enrollment</h3>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">How do I apply to the university?</h4>
              <p>You can apply online through our admissions portal. The application includes personal information, academic history, and supporting documents.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">What are the admission requirements?</h4>
              <p>Requirements vary by program. Generally, you need a high school diploma or equivalent, official transcripts, and standardized test scores (if applicable).</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">When is the application deadline?</h4>
              <p>We offer rolling admissions throughout the year. However, priority deadlines are March 1 for fall semester and October 1 for spring semester.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 mb-4">
            <div class="white-box">
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Academic Questions</h3>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">How do I register for classes?</h4>
              <p>You can register through the student portal during your assigned registration period. Check your registration date in the academic calendar.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">Can I change my major?</h4>
              <p>Yes, you can submit a major change request through the student portal. Contact your academic advisor to discuss your options.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">What is the withdrawal policy?</h4>
              <p>You can withdraw from a course before the withdrawal deadline with a "W" grade. Check the academic calendar for specific dates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 mb-4">
            <div class="white-box">
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Financial Questions</h3>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">How much is tuition?</h4>
              <p>Undergraduate tuition is $250 per credit hour. Graduate tuition is $350 per credit hour. Additional fees may apply.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">What financial aid is available?</h4>
              <p>We offer federal financial aid, scholarships, grants, and student loans. Complete the FAFSA to determine your eligibility.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">Can I set up a payment plan?</h4>
              <p>Yes, we offer flexible payment plans that allow you to spread tuition costs over several months with no interest.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 mb-4">
            <div class="white-box">
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Technical Questions</h3>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">What are the technical requirements?</h4>
              <p>You need a computer with internet access, a modern web browser, and basic software like Microsoft Office or equivalent.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">I forgot my password. How do I reset it?</h4>
              <p>Click "Forgot Password" on the login page and follow the instructions to reset your password via email.</p>

              <h4 class="h4 mt-4">Who do I contact for technical support?</h4>
              <p>Contact the IT Help Desk at 1-800-555-TECH or email techsupport@apus.edu for technical assistance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12">
            <div class="white-box">
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3">Still Have Questions?</h3>
              <p>If you can't find the answer you're looking for, contact us directly.</p>
              <a href="/contact-us.html" class="btn-main btn-sm">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
